title: Schedule for Thursday, October 22, 2015 (United States Senate Democrats)
text: ( Source : United States Senate Democrats ) The Senate stands adjourned until 10:00am on Thursday, October 22 , 2015 . Following any Leader remarks, the Senate will resume consideration of S.754, Cybersecurity Information Sharing Act of 2015,
